articleTitle: Nach Horror-Unfall: Golf-Star Woods in anderes Krankenhaus verlegt
articleTitleTranslated: After a horror accident: Golf star Woods moved to another hospital
articleContent: Zwei Tage nach seinem schweren Autounfall wurde Tiger Woods in ein anderes Spital gebracht. Infos zu seinem Zustand gab es keine.
articleContentTranslated: Two days after his serious car accident, Tiger Woods was taken to another hospital. There was no information about his condition.
